{"tid":703462,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Beef & Liberty 食評","createTime":"2018-06-15T18:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T21:55:37.000Z","uid":175988,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9eba511fd472b2428f0a3896ff645c9865758c78","tid":703462,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>Beef &amp; Liberty @ HKIA</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aN2ISKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaN2ISKz.jpg&h=aaddbef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Cheese Burger</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMedium rare 嘅 beef patty 稔滑得嚟帶咬口，肉厚多汁，油潤甘香，外層caramalization恰到好處，焦香而唔苦澀<br />\n<br />\n麵包鬆軟，牛油香夠，內層toast得微脆，外面光澤吸引，整體夠挺身，可以hold到啲fillings<br />\n<br />\n焦糖洋蒽嘅natural sweetness 平衡牛肉嘅肥膩，經典配搭無得輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗價錢稍貴(ard $120 for burger only)，今次真喺諗唔到有咩缺點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 絕對係我喺香港食過最好食嘅gourmet burger之一，絕對屌打Burgeroom同Triple O，甚至稍贏The Butchers Club，真心值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"880bd2ca067c6a708ec7cf0dfd1441dc5874ae93","tid":703462,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9eba511fd472b2428f0a3896ff645c9865758c78","tid":703462,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>Beef &amp; Liberty @ HKIA</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aN2ISKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaN2ISKz.jpg&h=aaddbef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Cheese Burger</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMedium rare 嘅 beef patty 稔滑得嚟帶咬口，肉厚多汁，油潤甘香，外層caramalization恰到好處，焦香而唔苦澀<br />\n<br />\n麵包鬆軟，牛油香夠，內層toast得微脆，外面光澤吸引，整體夠挺身，可以hold到啲fillings<br /